 don't know, now you're asking something - you see, at an early age those days you were taught to dress and undress yourself, at a very early age, there was mamby-pamby about those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7429570 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 Do you remember how early you dressed and undressed yourself?
