\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7429570 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 At this stage how much were you seeing of your own father?
