\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7429570 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 Did he sort of take you out without your real mother?
