\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7429570 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 Did you have any tasks you had to carry out regularly at home to help your foster father or mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10502885 JF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 
Oh yes, I used to have to clean all the shoes, he'd got about ten pairs, and he wouldn't have a - pair of shoes on twice without cleaning. So that was a regular job. I had a dog - which was had to be washed and - c
leaned and - his collar - cleaned up you know, so that the - foster father could take him out - at night. And I had to do the windows, and to gain - extra coppers well I used to sweep the yard and the neighbours yards and so on round about you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7429570 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 How long did you continue to do these tasks, did you go on after you left school?
