 early age. You see, you was always taught not to be afraid, you see. You wasn't to be afraid of the dark. You didn't go to bed with a - a lamp or light. The - you was - it was part of your - character building. You wasn't to be afraid. There was nothing 
to be afraid of. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid25946\charrsid6829132 That\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132  how we went you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7429570 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 What room did you bath in?
