\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7429570 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 You did have presents though, you said you had a dog, was this very unusual?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7429570 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 What, to have a dog?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10502885 JF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 No, as a birthday present?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10502885 JF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 Oh yes, I had him - when I should be about five or six. Just on the understanding that you looked after it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7429570 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 Did you ever have other birthday presents?
