\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10502885 JF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 
Yes. We used to play dominoes. Of an evening, with - along with this - fellow that used to work for them. In fact he was treated more or less like a - another son, but he was a lot older than me you see. But he used 
to go in and out the house and they'd regard him more or less - as a son, not to live there, but he used to go in and out and as he pleased himself, apart from his - his working hours. Sometimes at night he - we should - the four of us'd sit - round the t
able and play dominoes and so on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7429570 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 Were there any books in the house?
