Oh well quite a bit. But - he - you see, he'd never been married or anything you see and - he'd just sit down there and we - we'd sit and talk, he'd sit in the armchair, I used to sit on a little stool against his knee and 
- we should talk about various things, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7429570 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 Do you remember a funeral in the family?
