A funeral in the family. Well - no. No, I don't think I did, not 'til the - later years. Apart from - when this - younger brother of mine died, I can rememb
er - him dying you know. That was at me own - parents house of course. I can remember him dying. But - but not the older brother of course, because I was only about one when he - yes, I can remember him dying.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7429570 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10426719\charrsid6829132 Did you go to the funeral?
